com.sap.cloud.sdk.cloudplatform.auditlog

Interface AuditLog

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultLoggerAuditLog, ScpCfAuditLog, ScpNeoAuditLog

    public interface AuditLog
    Interface for audit logging.

    Important: For performance reasons, use only efficiently for logging of relevant events. The logging methods follow SAP's security standards:

    • SEC-215 "SAP software shall be able to log security relevant events."
    • SEC-254 "SAP software shall log read access to sensitive personal data."
    • SEC-257 "SAP software shall be able to log changes to configuration data."
    • SEC-265 "SAP software shall log changes to personal data."
